^W310     The domain comprises eight settlements.  Scattered throughout the country, these towns have an average population of 3,000, though about 5,000 people live in the shadow of Caer Callin.  Not only does everyone in the kingdom train for the militia, but also quite a few retired adventurers and mercenaries dwell in fair Aerenwe.  Currently we have available: 1 unit of irregulars and 1 unit of elite infantry.  All of them will muster willingly, if it comes to war.
